<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="no-js">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1"> 
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"> 
    <title>Blueprint: On Scroll Effect Layout</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Blueprint: On Scroll Effect Layout" />
    <meta name="keywords" content="on scroll, effect, slide in, layout, template, transition, javascript" />
    <meta name="author" content="Codrops" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="../favicon.ico">
    
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "default.css" %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "component.css" %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "modernizr.custom.js" %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <header class="clearfix">
        <span>The Heartbeat of Your Company<span></span></span>
        <h1>FooFoBerry</h1>
        <nav>
          <a href="#services" data-info="What is it?"><span>Previous Blueprint</span></a>
          <a href="#choose" data-info="Why Use it?"><span>Next Blueprint</span></a>
          <a href="#team" data-info="The Team"><span>Next Blueprint</span></a>
          <a href="#test" data-info="Testimonials"><span>Next Blueprint</span></a>
          <a href="" class="hide">
          <a href="/auth/github" data-info="Sign In"><span>Next Blueprint</span></a>
          
        </nav>
      </header> 
      <center/><%= image_tag("a3.jpg") %></center>
      <div id="cbp-so-scroller" class="cbp-so-scroller">
        <section class="cbp-so-section">
          <article class="cbp-so-side cbp-so-side-left">
            <h2>What Is It?</h2>
            <p>FooFoBerry is a dashboard that provides your development team with a real-time feed from Gitbhub, Travis CI, Pivotal Tracker and Code Climate that lets you gauge quality of your code and the speed of your project</p>
          </article>
          <figure class="cbp-so-side cbp-so-side-right">
            <a name="services"></a><%= image_tag("1-tablet.png") %>
          </figure>
        </section>
        <section class="cbp-so-section">
          <figure class="cbp-so-side cbp-so-side-left">
            <a name="choose"></a><%= image_tag("2-tablet.png") %>
          </figure>
          <article class="cbp-so-side cbp-so-side-right">
            <h2>Why Use It?</h2>
            <p>Unlike UI/UX projects, backend development projects live in a cloud somewhere between a laptop, github and project management software like Pivtoal Tracker and Rally. FooFoBerry gives your projects a home where progress is easily tracked and wins are able to celebrated by the team </p>
          </article>
        </section>
        <section class="cbp-so-section">
          <article class="cbp-so-side cbp-so-side-left">
            <h2>The Team</h2>
            <p>Based out of Denver Co, FooFoBerry is a small development studio headed up by 4 grads from Gschool. We specialize in beautifully simple and usable Web Design, Premium websites and apps.</p>
          </article>
          <figure class="cbp-so-side cbp-so-side-right">
            <a name="team"></a><%= image_tag("3-tablet.png") %>
          </figure>
        </section>
        <section class="cbp-so-section">
          <figure class="cbp-so-side cbp-so-side-left">
            <a name="test"></a><%= image_tag("4-tablet.png") %>
          </figure>
          <article class="cbp-so-side cbp-so-side-right">
            <h2>Testimonial</h2>
            <p>Billy Griffin owner of world Famous Billy's BBQ and avid cat lover uses FooFoBerry for his national chain of Restaurants:<br/><br/> <i>"I keep track of the progress of our new online ordering system through the 'Berry'. Can't live without it!</i></p>
          </article>
        </section>
        <center><h2><a href="#top" data-info="Back to Top"><span>back to top</span></a><h2></center>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script src="js/classie.js"></script>
    <script src="js/cbpScroller.js"></script>
    <script>
      new cbpScroller( document.getElementById( 'cbp-so-scroller' ) );
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
